nombre: Upcountry Hospitality in the 'Auwai Suite
descripción:
The 'Auwai Suite is a lovely, self-contained apartment at the back of our historic Waimea Guest House built in the 1800's. This suite is named for the 100-year-old Hawaiian irrigation canal that runs through the property.

It has a full kitchen, dining area, beautifully tiled bathroom, bedroom with queen bed and two window seats, and a shared garden.

This is the most popular suite in Waimea Guest House and is great for extended stays.
